Localisation - adaptation of a system for a specific reiong
language translations, characters and scripts, units, currencies, time and date formats, meaning of colors and symbols, suitability of images, legal requirements.

Interationalization - designing a system to be prepared to make localization possible and easy.

"Internationalization is not a feature, it is an architecture".

I18n - Internalization
L10n - Localization
a11y - accessibility